    "Html": "\r\n<p>If you wish to change the tempo into a midi file here are the steps to do it.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2b91af; font-size:9.5pt\">MidiEventCollection</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">reponse =\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">new</span> <span style=\"color:#2b91af\">MidiEventCollection</span>(1, 120);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; //<span style=\"color:#00ff00\">---&gt;the midi collection</span></span><span style=\"color:#00ff00; font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">///</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:green; font-size:9.5pt\"> Add this line to your midi collection.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">reponse.AddEvent(<span style=\"color:blue\">new</span>\r\n<span style=\"color:#2b91af\">TempoEvent</span>(Micro_second_calculator_for_quater_note(bpm),0),0);&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; //<span style=\"color:#00ff00\">----&gt;the tempo event</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-size:9.5pt\">EXPLANATION</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&agrave;</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">(<strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">bpm</span></em></strong>),0),0) = &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; bpm is the speed of the song in\r\n<em>Beats Per Minute</em></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&agrave;</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">(bpm),<strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">0</span></em></strong>),0) =&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 0 is the delta time where the tempo\r\n event begins</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&agrave;</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">(bpm),0),<strong><em><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">1</span></em></strong>) =&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 1 is the track number that will kept\r\n this information </span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">///</span><span style=\"color:green; font-size:9.5pt\">\r\n</span><span style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">&lt;summary&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">///</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:green; font-size:9.5pt\"> Method to calculate the number of microseconds for a quater note for a precise BPM.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">///</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:green; font-size:9.5pt\">\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">&lt;/summary&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">///</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:green; font-size:9.5pt\">\r\n</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">&lt;param name=&quot;bpm&quot;&gt;&lt;/param&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">///</span><span style=\"color:green; font-size:9.5pt\">\r\n</span><span style=\"color:gray; font-size:9.5pt\">&lt;returns&gt;&lt;/returns&gt;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:blue; font-size:9.5pt\">private</span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">static</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">int</span> Micro_second_calculator_for_quater_note (<span style=\"color:blue\">double</span> bpm)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#00ff00\">//----&gt;the static method</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">{</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"color:green; font-size:9.5pt\">//one micro second = 0,000001 second</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"color:green\">//So, multiplication by 1000000 (1 million)</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">const</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">int</span> microsecond= 1000000;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">int</span> answer = 0;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">double</span> temp=60;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; temp = temp / bpm;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; temp = temp * microsecond;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; answer = (<span style=\"color:blue\">int</span>)temp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n<span style=\"color:blue\">return</span> answer;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">}</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\"EN-CA\" style=\"font-size:9.5pt\">Distorsion13 says:&nbsp; tada!</span></p>\r\n",
